                </a>

                <!-- Card 3 -->
                <a href="https://studentaid.gov/resources/prepare-for-college/students/budgeting/creating-your-budget" class="card" target="_blank">
                    <div class="card-title">Creating Your Budget</div>
                    <div class="card-description">
                        Explore how to create a budget for college and manage your finances with tips from Federal Student Aid.
                    </div>
                </a>

                <!-- Card 4 -->
                <a href="https://www.husson.edu/online/blog/2023/04/money-saving-tips-for-students" class="card" target="_blank">
                    <div class="card-title">Money-Saving Tips for Students</div>
                    <div class="card-description">
                        Check out valuable money-saving tips tailored for college students to make the most of your budget.
                    </div>
                </a>

                <!-- Card 5 -->
