                    <div class="card-description">
                        Learn practical strategies for financial wellness to stay ahead with your college budget.
                    </div>
                </a>

                <!-- Card 6 -->
                <a href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/enochomololu/2023/09/03/7-money-saving-hacks-for-college-students-budgeting-tips-and-tricks/" class="card" target="_blank">
